  "source": "// Tuple return and destructuring demo.\nseiyaku TupleReturnDemo {\n  fn pair(a: int, b: int) -> (int, int) {\n    let t = (a + 1, b + 1);\n    return t;\n  }\n\n  kotoage fn compute() -> (int, int) {\n    let p = pair(3, 5);\n    // Destructure using numeric field access\n    return (p.0, p.1);\n  }\n}\n",
